tection officer shall be designated on the basis of professional qualities and, in particular, expert knowledge of data protection law and practices and the ability to fulfil the tasks referred to in Article 39.\n\n6.   The data protection officer may be a staff member of the controller or processor, or fulfil the tasks on the basis of a service contract.\n\n7.   The controller or the processor shall publish the contact details of the data protection officer and communicate them to the supervisory authority.<turn|>\n<|turn>model\n<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>\n<processModel>\n  <pools>\n    <pool id=\"Participant_ControllerOrProcessor_Art37\" name=\"Controller or Processor\" poolType=\"active\" processRef=\"Process_ControllerOrProcessor_Art37\" />\n    <pool id=\"Participant_SupervisoryAuthority_Art37\" name=\"Supervisory Authority\" poolType=\"passive\" />\n  </pools>\n  <lanes />\n  <tasks>\n    <task id=\"SendTask_NotifyAuthority_Art37\" name=\"Notify supervisory authority\" type=\"sendTask\" poolRef=\"Participant_ControllerOrProcessor_Art37\" />\n    <task id=\"Task_AppointServiceContractDPO_Art37\" name=\"Appoint service-contract DPO\" type=\"task\" poolRef=\"Participant_ControllerOrProcessor_Art37\" />\n    <task id=\"Task_AppointStaffDPO_Art37\" name=\"Appoint staff-member DPO\" type=\"task\" poolRef=\"Participant_ControllerOrProcessor_Art37\" />\n    <task id=\"Task_AssessAdditionalDesignation_Art37\" name=\"Check optional or law-required designation\" type=\"task\" poolRef=\"Participant_ControllerOrProcessor_Art37\" />\n    <task id=\"Task_AssessLargeScale_Art37\" name=\"Check large-scale sensitive or criminal-data processing\" type=\"task\" poolRef=\"Participant_ControllerOrProcessor_Art37\" />\n    <task id=\"Task_AssessMonitoring_Art37\" name=\"Check large-scale monitoring\" type=\"task\" poolRef=\"Participant_ControllerOrProcessor_Art37\" />\n    <task id=\"Task_AssessPublic_Art37\" name=\"Check public-authority status\" type=\"task\" poolRef=\